Mary Louise Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Louise_Wilson 0 Mary Louise Wilson (born November 12, 1931) is an American stage, film and television actress, singer, and comedian. She was born in New Haven, Connecticut, but raised in New Orleans, Louisiana. She was married to fellow actor Albert “Chibbie” Cibelli for three years before the union ended in divorce.
